{"id":230,"date":"2007-06-19T12:45:14","date_gmt":"2007-06-19T12:45:14","guid":{"rendered":"http://192.168.5.119/2.2/?p=230"},"modified":"2007-06-19T12:45:14","modified_gmt":"2007-06-19T12:45:14","slug":"thunderbird%e7%ac%94%e8%ae%b02%e5%88%99","status":"publish","link":"https://xbeta.info/thunderbird%e7%ac%94%e8%ae%b02%e5%88%99.htm","title":{"rendered":"Thunderbird笔记2则"},"content":{"rendered":"<div><font COLOR=\"#A6A6A6\">作者:xbeta　版本:070619/070619　出自:</font><a TITLE=\"善用佳软:宣传最经典的免费软件及应用技巧。文章欢迎署名转载\" HREF=\"http://xbeta.info/\" TARGET=\"_blank\"><font COLOR=\"#CC3333\">善用</font><font COLOR=\"#339999\">佳软</font><font COLOR=\"#A6A6A6\">http://xbeta.info</font></a></div>\n<div><img STYLE=\"FLOAT: left; MARGIN: 4px\" SRC=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/img/app-icons/thunderbird.png\">&nbsp;</div>\n<p>1. 解决签名位置问题。</p>\n<p>\n　　以前，回复别人时，签名位于邮件最后（即引用内容之后），一直不习惯，但忍了。近期发现其实有配置，其实就在：Account<br />\nSettings→xx账户→Composition &#038; Addressing中，&#8221; and place my<br />\nsignature……&#8221;。『<a HREF=\"http://forums.mozine.cn/index.php?s=ffcfa681332dd535cbc8105213d3db8d&#038;showtopic=4199\" TARGET=\"_blank\">此文</a>』对“<b>默认的光标位置在引用信息之后，如何设置到前面？</b>”有答复，但未提及此点。Thunderbird<br />\nV1.5不支持此设置？</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>2. 解决edit html source问题。</p>\n<p>　　以前，编写邮件用html格式时，无法编辑源代码，有时不方便。</p>\n<p>　　今天找到了解决办法：</p>\n<p>　　简言之 Ctrl+A，Alt+I H。</p>\n<p>　　解说一下就是，全选编辑内容，菜单Insert→HTML。</p>\n<p>　　也可以用扩展来实现：<a HREF=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/thunderbird/addon/756\" TARGET=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/thunderbird/addon/756</a><br />\n（请注意版本）<br />\n　　推荐用前者，不推荐用扩展。</p>\n<p>></iframe></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>作者:xbeta　版本:070619/070619　出自:善用佳软http://xbeta.info &#038;nbs [&hellip;]</p>\n","protected":false},"author":15,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":["旧.网络相关","未分类"],"tags":["all"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/230"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/users/15"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/comments?post=230"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/230/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/media?parent=230"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/categories?post=230"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/tags?post=230"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https://api.w.org/{rel}","templated":true}]},"wp_type":"post"}